## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

### Port in use:
```bash
PORT=3001 npm run dev
```

### TypeScript errors:
```bash
rm -rf dist node_modules
npm install
npm run build
```

### API key issues:
```bash
echo $ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
echo $OPENAI_API_KEY
```

